invalid type: string "Colophon \nThe animal on the cover of Hands-On Large Language Models is a red\nkangaroo (Osphranter rufus). They are the largest of all kangaroos, with a\nbody length that can get up to a little over 5 feet and a tail as long as 3 feet.\nThey are very fast and can hop to speeds over 35 miles per hour. They can\nd Contrastive Training, What Is\nContrastive Learning?\nn_p\netc: